item.title: Blorg Bread Baker
item.description: The hand-crafted Blorg Bread Baker™ enhances any kitchen. Produced from 100% post-consumer recycled materials you’ll never once think… wait a minute, I’m baking my bread in other people’s refuse. Features Bakes artisanal bread Slices Doubles as a bread-box Controllable-Anywhere, part of the Internet Of Things Some versions may include a BetaMax™ video tape interface.
